The parser tool requires a `source` parameter and supports an optional `options` object. Since it failed with an INVALID_INPUT error expecting CSV format, but our input file is "data/input.json" (JSON format), I need to specify the format in the options.

I'll execute the parser again with the format explicitly set to "json" in the options parameter.

<tool_call>data_processing_parser
{
  "source": "data/input.json",
  "options": {
    "format": "json"
  }
}
</tool_call>
